window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The time for wedding bells to ring has arrived in Eternal Dominion.</p> <p>Xeal must make his final preparations for what is sure to be a unique experience in marrying three princesses from very different backgrounds and families, as there will be no going back once it is done! Especially with three more waiting brides and the fulfillment of their duties as nobles to take care of after the wedding.</p>"; 
